            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratori</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Caes</abbr><ex>ari</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arco</ex></expan> A<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>ur</abbr><ex>elio</ex></expan> A</supplied>n<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>ton</abbr><ex>ino</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="2"/>Pio <expan><abbr>Fel</abbr><ex>ici</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usto</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>Par</abbr><ex>thico</ex></expan></supplied> <expan><abbr>B<supplied reason="lost">r</supplied>it</abbr><ex>annico</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Germ</abbr><ex>anico</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pont</abbr><ex>ifici</ex></expan> maximo <lb n="4"/>et Iuliae <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustae</ex></expan> matri <lb n="5"/>castroru<surplus>u</surplus>m <lb n="6"/>ob victoriam <lb n="7"/>Germanicam
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Datierung: bald nach dem Sieg Caracallas über die Germanen im September(?) 213 n. Chr. (B): CIL XIII: kleinere Abweichungen in der Lesung. Buchstaben sind heute sekundär ausgemalt. Autopsie: R. Wiegels; Hauptbearbeiterin: B. Esch.</p>
            </div>
